January shouldn’t be about punishing yourself, whatever some “new year, new you” advocates would have you believe. And if, like many hundreds of thousands of others, you’re planning on going plant-based for veganuary, may we suggest the best way to get excited about your new food regime is by buying an excellent vegan cookbook. There have never been more on the shelves! Below, we round up a selection of our favourites, sure to suit every style and palate. Enjoy your plant-based feasting!